# Triage stage: classify the message. op://classify is a BUNDLED compute —
# the colocated classify.js ships with this package and is built to wasm at
# `txco apply` time. The classifier merges `category` + `urgency` into the
# envelope before scope 200 runs.
WHEN ._txc.web.req.url.path =~ /^\/support(\/|$)/
EXEC "op://classify"
